WEBVTT

00:00:10.277 --> 00:00:11.278
[AKATSUCHI] <i>Hey, stop!</i>

00:00:26.293 --> 00:00:29.429
Master... My dearest father...

00:00:29.463 --> 00:00:32.766
[KU] <i>The test subject is</i>
<i>now ready.</i>

00:00:32.799 --> 00:00:34.968
We're merely awaiting your
orders!

00:00:35.936 --> 00:00:37.137
[ALL] (GASP)

00:00:37.938 --> 00:00:39.139
Old Man Ohnoki...?!

00:00:39.940 --> 00:00:41.141
It can't be...!

00:00:42.776 --> 00:00:44.111
(CONFIDENT CHUCKLE)

00:00:50.117 --> 00:01:00.127
♪♪ [JAPANESE THEME MUSIC]

00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:10.170
♪♪ [JAPANESE THEME MUSIC]

00:01:10.204 --> 00:01:20.113
♪♪ [JAPANESE THEME MUSIC]

00:01:20.147 --> 00:01:30.190
♪♪ [JAPANESE THEME MUSIC]

00:01:30.224 --> 00:01:40.133
♪♪ [JAPANESE THEME MUSIC]

00:01:40.167 --> 00:01:50.177
♪♪ [JAPANESE THEME MUSIC]

00:01:50.210 --> 00:02:00.120
♪♪ [JAPANESE THEME MUSIC]

00:02:00.153 --> 00:02:10.197
♪♪ [JAPANESE THEME MUSIC]

00:02:10.230 --> 00:02:20.107
♪♪ [JAPANESE THEME MUSIC]

00:02:20.140 --> 00:02:26.113
♪♪ [JAPANESE THEME MUSIC]

00:02:39.493 --> 00:02:40.661
(STUNNED)

00:02:45.699 --> 00:02:47.467
What is going on?! Tell me!

00:02:50.337 --> 00:02:51.138
Hey, Old Man!

00:02:54.675 --> 00:02:57.177
Damn it! Say something! Now!

00:02:58.979 --> 00:03:00.314
(DISCOMFORT)

00:03:02.649 --> 00:03:05.452
You'd better watch your
language, child. You hear?

00:03:05.485 --> 00:03:06.620
[BORUTO] <i>(ANGRY)</i>

00:03:06.653 --> 00:03:07.721
Boruto!

00:03:07.754 --> 00:03:09.056
(MENACING GROWL)

00:03:09.089 --> 00:03:10.190
(FRUSTRATED)

00:03:16.530 --> 00:03:18.165
I'm so sorry.

00:03:18.198 --> 00:03:21.235
So you mean the old man isn't
really on our side?!

00:03:21.268 --> 00:03:23.537
Yeah. It seems that we were
wrong about him.

00:03:23.570 --> 00:03:26.173
Hey! Don't do anything that'll
hurt them!

00:03:27.140 --> 00:03:29.476
Akatsuchi... stay out of
this.

00:03:29.977 --> 00:03:31.144
(SHOCKED)

00:03:31.979 --> 00:03:34.314
I'm doing this for your sake.

00:03:35.315 --> 00:03:36.984
(ANGRY)

00:03:37.017 --> 00:03:40.020
I'm doing all of this for the
sake of peace.

00:03:46.360 --> 00:03:51.164
(PHONE RINGING)

00:03:52.499 --> 00:03:53.500
Hello?

00:03:54.168 --> 00:03:55.636
[NARUTO] <i>Is this Kontsuchi?</i>

00:03:56.503 --> 00:03:57.704
[KONTSUCHI] <i>Yes.</i>

00:03:57.738 --> 00:03:58.639
Is Kurotsuchi there?

00:04:00.307 --> 00:04:01.341
[KONTSUCHI] I'm afraid Lady
Tsuchikage hasn't returned...

00:04:01.375 --> 00:04:03.744
<i>from her trip to the border</i>
<i>lands.</i>

00:04:03.777 --> 00:04:06.146
What? She hasn't come back
yet?

00:04:06.180 --> 00:04:09.283
Have you learned anything since
the last time we spoke?

00:04:09.316 --> 00:04:12.486
No... Nothing that would require
<i>immediate action.</i>

00:04:13.320 --> 00:04:14.321
I see.

00:04:15.622 --> 00:04:18.625
I'll contact you just as soon as
<i>Lady Tsuchikage returns.</i>

00:04:18.659 --> 00:04:21.128
Yes, I'd appreciate that.

00:04:21.161 --> 00:04:24.598
But just so you know, it might
not be for a while.

00:04:24.631 --> 00:04:25.332
[NARUTO] <i>Understood.</i>

00:04:25.999 --> 00:04:27.467
All right. Please excuse me.

00:04:32.306 --> 00:04:35.142
Excellent... Such a
good boy.

00:04:40.147 --> 00:04:41.815
So she wasn't there, huh?

00:04:41.849 --> 00:04:44.084
(SIGH) I'd really like
to believe...

00:04:44.117 --> 00:04:46.720
that they're doing something on
their end, but...

00:04:46.753 --> 00:04:49.156
I guess we'll just have to wait
to hear from Konohamaru.

00:04:49.823 --> 00:04:51.024
Yeah...

00:04:51.658 --> 00:04:54.194
[NARUTO] <i>Guess so.</i>

00:05:00.367 --> 00:05:01.134
(STUNNED)

00:05:08.342 --> 00:05:09.643
(STRUGGLING)

00:05:10.811 --> 00:05:12.813
Damn you!

00:05:12.846 --> 00:05:15.315
Where's Mitsuki now? Just give
him back!

00:05:16.149 --> 00:05:17.651
Be quiet. Keep still.

00:05:18.352 --> 00:05:20.120
(DISCOMFORT)

00:05:20.153 --> 00:05:21.655
They told me all about it...

00:05:22.489 --> 00:05:24.391
The abduction of the Hidden Leaf
genin...

00:05:24.424 --> 00:05:26.059
...and the attacks on these
kids...

00:05:26.093 --> 00:05:28.595
who came here looking for him...

00:05:28.629 --> 00:05:30.664
Was all of that... your doing?

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:35.135
<i>And... who the hell</i>
<i>are they?</i>

00:05:36.637 --> 00:05:39.306
On top of all that, Kurotsuchi's
missing, too.

00:05:42.809 --> 00:05:47.114
What's going on in the Stone?!
And why won't you say anything?!

00:05:47.147 --> 00:05:48.649
Silence, Akatsuchi!

00:05:49.316 --> 00:05:50.317
(STUNNED)

00:05:50.984 --> 00:05:54.321
(FRUSTRATED) Just answer him!

00:05:55.155 --> 00:05:57.191
[OHNOKI] Ku... release him.

00:05:57.491 --> 00:06:00.561
Yes.

00:06:00.594 --> 00:06:04.164
(STRUGGLING)

00:06:04.198 --> 00:06:07.067
What do you mean, it's for the
sake of peace?

00:06:07.100 --> 00:06:09.102
C'mon, explain yourself!

00:06:09.136 --> 00:06:12.172
I'm trying to avoid repeating
another tragedy.

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:14.441
Tragedy...?

00:06:14.474 --> 00:06:16.210
Five years ago...

00:06:16.243 --> 00:06:19.213
the Stone Village was attacked
by Rogue Ninja.

00:06:19.246 --> 00:06:23.150
Many young shinobi lost their
lives in that incident.

00:06:23.183 --> 00:06:27.287
And afterward, it became
extremely clear to me...

00:06:27.321 --> 00:06:30.490
I have to protect the
young lives that are our future.

00:06:30.991 --> 00:06:32.192
(TAKNE BACK)

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:37.197
Like us, you've been attacked,
haven't you? By the Otsutsuki?

00:06:38.532 --> 00:06:39.600
There's no predicting...

00:06:39.633 --> 00:06:43.537
When another terrifying enemy
like them will appear.

00:06:43.570 --> 00:06:44.705
And when it does...

00:06:44.738 --> 00:06:48.141
we mustn't let them take the
lives of our youth.

00:06:49.476 --> 00:06:51.044
To keep them safe...

00:06:51.078 --> 00:06:53.380
what we need to do is find
something else...

00:06:53.413 --> 00:06:56.550
...that is able to fight in
their place.

00:06:56.583 --> 00:06:59.653
You're saying that "something"
is these guys?

00:07:00.320 --> 00:07:01.989
<i>Yes.</i>

00:07:02.022 --> 00:07:03.891
What does all this have to do
with Mitsuki?!

00:07:03.924 --> 00:07:06.393
Why'd you take him away from
us?!

00:07:06.426 --> 00:07:10.297
Mitsuki will be helping me to
complete my plan.

00:07:10.330 --> 00:07:11.331
What?!

00:07:12.499 --> 00:07:16.003
Of course, Mitsuki decided
that of his own free will.

00:07:16.303 --> 00:07:17.304
No!

00:07:29.983 --> 00:07:31.251
[SEKIEI] <i>Mitsuki!</i>

00:07:31.285 --> 00:07:32.186
(NOTICES)

00:07:32.653 --> 00:07:34.821
There you are!

00:07:34.855 --> 00:07:37.157
Yes? You were looking
for me?

00:07:37.191 --> 00:07:40.661
Mhm, Lord Ku instructed me to
bring you to see him.

00:07:42.196 --> 00:07:45.499
To bring me to him? Or was it to
keep an eye on me?

00:07:46.667 --> 00:07:48.368
Well... yeah...

00:07:48.402 --> 00:07:52.206
Lord Ku's never met you, so he
doesn't know much about you.

00:07:52.239 --> 00:07:55.309
But when you do meet, I think
you'll get along quite well!

00:07:57.477 --> 00:07:58.478
I hope we do.

00:08:22.135 --> 00:08:23.637
This will be your room.

00:08:24.505 --> 00:08:25.305
(CONSIDERING)

00:08:28.342 --> 00:08:29.142
You like it?

00:08:31.178 --> 00:08:33.547
If it's missing something or if
there's anything you need...

00:08:33.580 --> 00:08:35.249
just let me know!

00:08:35.282 --> 00:08:36.483
All right.

00:08:36.517 --> 00:08:38.185
Now let's move on...

00:08:44.358 --> 00:08:45.158
(GASP)

00:08:49.863 --> 00:08:52.199
This is how the Akuta are
created.

00:08:54.001 --> 00:08:56.036
But... they aren't like us...

00:08:56.069 --> 00:08:59.540
since we possess a will of our
own.

00:08:59.573 --> 00:09:00.474
A will...

00:09:00.974 --> 00:09:02.142
<i>I told you, right?</i>

00:09:03.310 --> 00:09:05.746
I'm sure Lord Ku will explain...

00:09:05.779 --> 00:09:07.481
what the secret behind a will
is.

00:09:08.682 --> 00:09:10.250
When can I meet him?

00:09:10.284 --> 00:09:11.185
<i>Soon.</i>

00:09:12.653 --> 00:09:13.654
I can't wait.

00:09:16.323 --> 00:09:17.491
[MITSUKI] <i>There are so many...</i>

00:09:18.525 --> 00:09:20.060
Yeah, you're right!

00:09:20.093 --> 00:09:22.596
Soon, we'll have more than all
of the shinobi

00:09:22.629 --> 00:09:24.431
in the Hidden StoneVillage.

00:09:24.464 --> 00:09:25.165
(IMPRESSED)

00:09:26.200 --> 00:09:28.635
But... the Master says we
still need more...

00:09:29.636 --> 00:09:30.637
(CONSIDERING) Hm?

00:09:31.338 --> 00:09:32.706
We need more...

00:09:32.739 --> 00:09:36.043
in order to protect the young
people of the village.

00:09:36.076 --> 00:09:39.580
So... you're saying they and
those like you...

00:09:39.613 --> 00:09:41.048
will die in their place?

00:09:41.081 --> 00:09:42.583
Die in their place?

00:09:42.616 --> 00:09:45.552
[KOKUYOU] <i>Hey!</i>

00:09:45.586 --> 00:09:49.122
There you are. Don't
wander around so much.

00:09:49.156 --> 00:09:51.491
Lord Ku asked me to show him
around.

00:09:52.326 --> 00:09:53.493
(ANGRY)

00:09:54.328 --> 00:09:56.496
Let's go. I'll show you my
room.

00:10:01.335 --> 00:10:04.738
Just how long are we
going to let him live, anyway?

00:10:04.771 --> 00:10:08.375
I say we oughta just cut
him up already.

00:10:08.408 --> 00:10:10.477
If you'd like, I'd be happy to
do it!

00:10:12.145 --> 00:10:13.647
Wait for Lord Ku's orders.

00:10:19.486 --> 00:10:20.487
(STUNNED)

00:10:21.655 --> 00:10:24.157
What are you talking about?!
Mitsuki is helping you?!

00:10:24.992 --> 00:10:26.994
(FRIGHTENED)

00:10:27.027 --> 00:10:29.796
Uh, Sarada? Maybe you
shouldn't upset them...

00:10:29.830 --> 00:10:32.199
Yeah, I know that. But...

00:10:32.833 --> 00:10:34.468
Just take us to Mitsuki!

00:10:34.501 --> 00:10:37.271
I'm sorry, but doing that isn't
possible.

00:10:37.304 --> 00:10:38.305
Why not?!

00:10:39.439 --> 00:10:43.143
You see, the plan is now
entering its final stages.

00:10:43.177 --> 00:10:45.746
And Mitsuki's cooperation will
be essential...

00:10:45.779 --> 00:10:47.714
if we're going to make it work.

00:10:47.748 --> 00:10:48.782
(fFRUSTRATED)

00:10:48.815 --> 00:10:50.050
Just hold on!

00:10:50.083 --> 00:10:51.552
If he learns you harmed us...

00:10:51.585 --> 00:10:53.921
or the Leaf shinobi sent after
Mitsuki...

00:10:53.954 --> 00:10:55.889
Lord Seventh is gonna have to
take action!

00:10:55.923 --> 00:10:59.159
Of course. I'm well aware of
that.

00:10:59.193 --> 00:11:02.496
Initially, the plan was to do
everything completely in secret.

00:11:03.497 --> 00:11:06.233
I didn't imagine that I'd end up
having to deal...

00:11:06.266 --> 00:11:09.403
with you Leaf Shinobi.
However...

00:11:09.436 --> 00:11:13.473
...I have no alternative if I'm
going to proceed with my plan.

00:11:14.675 --> 00:11:16.910
Look, take us to see Mitsuki!

00:11:16.944 --> 00:11:19.880
I need to speak with him. Just
one more time.

00:11:19.913 --> 00:11:22.549
I have to speak with him!

00:11:22.583 --> 00:11:23.483
[BORUTO] <i>Please!</i>

00:11:24.518 --> 00:11:25.652
Please! Take me to him!

00:11:29.990 --> 00:11:31.325
No, we're done talking!

00:11:31.992 --> 00:11:34.161
(DISCOMFORT)

00:11:34.828 --> 00:11:37.664
(STRUGGLING) (COUGHING)

00:11:38.665 --> 00:11:40.167
(GASP) Lord Ohnoki!

00:11:40.667 --> 00:11:42.603
(STRUGGLING)

00:11:42.636 --> 00:11:45.739
Just behave yourselves for a
little while longer.

00:11:45.772 --> 00:11:48.375
I have no intention of hurting
you.

00:11:48.408 --> 00:11:49.309
Ku!

00:11:50.310 --> 00:11:51.311
(WORRIED)

00:11:53.313 --> 00:11:54.615
(ANNOYED)

00:11:54.648 --> 00:11:56.316
No way! Not gonna happen!

00:12:06.026 --> 00:12:07.194
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

00:12:09.863 --> 00:12:11.365
(DETERMINED)

00:12:14.535 --> 00:12:15.669
(FRUSTRATED)

00:12:15.702 --> 00:12:18.172
No! Ku, please, do not hurt him!

00:12:18.839 --> 00:12:20.440
(FRUSTRATED) Get him!

00:12:20.474 --> 00:12:21.742
(ATTACKING)

00:12:21.775 --> 00:12:24.077
(DODGING)

00:12:24.111 --> 00:12:25.345
Ku! Please don't!

00:12:26.346 --> 00:12:29.516
Don't worry, I've got this!
Human Boulder!

00:12:31.018 --> 00:12:34.054
(KNOCKED DOWN)

00:12:36.356 --> 00:12:37.357
(SCOFF)

00:12:38.192 --> 00:12:39.493
(ATTENTION IS CAUGHT)

00:12:39.526 --> 00:12:41.361
(ATTACKING GROWL)

00:12:43.397 --> 00:12:44.431
Rasengan!

00:12:44.464 --> 00:12:47.801
(HIT BY ATTACK)

00:12:47.835 --> 00:12:50.170
Cha!

00:12:53.507 --> 00:12:55.809
Their weakness... It's their
mask!

00:12:55.843 --> 00:12:57.911
(MENACING GROWLS)

00:12:57.945 --> 00:12:59.513
They just keep coming!

00:13:00.848 --> 00:13:02.049
Earth Style! Barrier!

00:13:02.683 --> 00:13:03.684
Earth Dome Prison!

00:13:04.351 --> 00:13:06.053
(SHOCKED)

00:13:09.189 --> 00:13:12.226
Earth Style! Earth Golem Jutsu!

00:13:15.863 --> 00:13:18.599
Go now! Make a run for it!

00:13:18.632 --> 00:13:19.533
[BORUTO] <i>Akatsuchi!</i>

00:13:20.033 --> 00:13:21.502
Go on! Hurry!

00:13:21.535 --> 00:13:22.603
[BORUTO] <i>Thank you!</i>

00:13:22.636 --> 00:13:23.804
Time to split up, guys!

00:13:23.837 --> 00:13:25.305
Meet back at our camp!

00:13:25.339 --> 00:13:26.340
Got it!

00:13:26.673 --> 00:13:28.408
Enough!

00:13:28.442 --> 00:13:29.610
(SHOCKED)

00:13:29.643 --> 00:13:31.578
Atomic Dismantling Jutsu!

00:13:31.612 --> 00:13:32.513
(WORRIED)

00:13:33.013 --> 00:13:34.481
Is that-?!

00:13:34.515 --> 00:13:35.649
(DETERMINED)

00:13:35.682 --> 00:13:36.750
(PUNCHING)

00:13:36.783 --> 00:13:38.185
(SWINGING WEAPONS)

00:13:38.685 --> 00:13:39.686
(SLAM)

00:13:45.859 --> 00:13:46.994
(CRINGING)

00:13:47.027 --> 00:13:48.362
(WORRIED)

00:13:48.395 --> 00:13:50.230
(FRIGHTENED)

00:13:51.565 --> 00:13:52.366
(FRUSTRATED)

00:13:54.368 --> 00:13:55.903
Lord Ohnoki!

00:13:55.936 --> 00:13:57.337
(FRUSTRATED)

00:13:58.372 --> 00:13:59.506
Boruto...

00:14:00.841 --> 00:14:01.975
(CURIOUS GROWL)

00:14:02.009 --> 00:14:03.644
(HITTING THE GROUND)

00:14:03.677 --> 00:14:08.515
Damn it! (STRUGGLING)

00:14:15.022 --> 00:14:16.223
[SEKIEI] <i>(SURPRISED)</i>

00:14:19.726 --> 00:14:21.495
[SEKIEI] <i>Something happen?</i>

00:14:21.528 --> 00:14:23.697
Never mind that. Just
keep an eye on him.

00:14:24.565 --> 00:14:26.366
Oh, okay. C'mon.

00:14:26.867 --> 00:14:28.035
Right.

00:14:35.175 --> 00:14:36.510
[SEKIEI] <i>This is my room.</i>

00:14:37.544 --> 00:14:39.313
You... drew these?

00:14:39.346 --> 00:14:42.216
Yep! They're drawings
of my friends!

00:14:45.185 --> 00:14:47.087
The Master created us...

00:14:47.120 --> 00:14:51.658
so that he could protect the
people he cherishes.

00:14:51.692 --> 00:14:55.529
That's why... I want to create
friendships worth protecting.

00:15:00.400 --> 00:15:03.504
Humans become stronger when they
have someone to protect, right?

00:15:04.338 --> 00:15:05.339
(SHOCKED)

00:15:07.374 --> 00:15:08.175
That's right.

00:15:12.846 --> 00:15:15.682
Now... I have one more friend!

00:15:21.855 --> 00:15:23.524
(STUMBLING)

00:15:29.196 --> 00:15:30.764
[KUROTSUCHI] <i>Who're you?</i>

00:15:30.797 --> 00:15:32.232
(STARTLED)

00:15:34.067 --> 00:15:38.338
You're... Lady Tsuchikage...
aren't you?!

00:15:38.672 --> 00:15:40.140
(GASP)

00:15:40.174 --> 00:15:42.509
[KUROTSUCHI] <i>Are you...</i>
<i>Shikamaru's son?</i>

00:15:43.343 --> 00:15:45.512
Yes, ma'am. My name is
Shikadai.

00:15:46.847 --> 00:15:48.215
What're you doing here?

00:15:48.849 --> 00:15:50.050
Oh. Well...

00:15:54.555 --> 00:15:56.190
Do you ever draw, Mitsuki?

00:15:56.857 --> 00:15:58.225
No, not really...

00:15:59.026 --> 00:16:00.227
(CURIOUS)

00:16:00.727 --> 00:16:02.229
Okay, we're all ready.

00:16:02.563 --> 00:16:03.363
All right!

00:16:03.864 --> 00:16:04.998
Ready?

00:16:05.032 --> 00:16:06.099
For what?

00:16:06.133 --> 00:16:07.334
Your examination.

00:16:08.535 --> 00:16:09.336
(CONCERNED)

00:16:10.003 --> 00:16:12.172
Come on, it's this way.

00:16:13.173 --> 00:16:14.508
I'll come with you, too!

00:16:32.860 --> 00:16:34.228
(PLEASED)

00:16:39.533 --> 00:16:40.534
Huh?

00:16:41.535 --> 00:16:42.336
What is that?

00:16:43.504 --> 00:16:45.205
A Curse Mark?!

00:16:57.551 --> 00:16:58.352
[KUROTSUCHI] <i>I see...</i>

00:16:59.720 --> 00:17:01.922
Naruto had asked me for my
help.

00:17:01.955 --> 00:17:04.791
He told me you
might be coming this way.

00:17:04.825 --> 00:17:07.094
And to make sure you got back
safe.

00:17:07.127 --> 00:17:08.195
Lord Seventh did that?

00:17:09.530 --> 00:17:12.366
I see... So he saw all this
coming.

00:17:13.734 --> 00:17:15.936
I really screwed everything up.

00:17:15.969 --> 00:17:19.573
To think that I'd end up being
locked in here.

00:17:19.606 --> 00:17:22.342
Something's going on here.
What's happening in the Stone?

00:17:23.510 --> 00:17:27.047
The Third Tsuchikage says that
he's doing all this for peace.

00:17:27.514 --> 00:17:28.515
(SIGH)

00:17:29.850 --> 00:17:32.953
I don't know what's happening
to Boruto and the others.

00:17:32.986 --> 00:17:36.190
If you know something, could
you please tell me?

00:17:36.690 --> 00:17:37.691
Yes...

00:17:39.026 --> 00:17:41.261
This whole thing began

00:17:41.295 --> 00:17:46.767
when I rejected an idea that my
grandfather proposed.

00:17:46.800 --> 00:17:48.936
[KUROTSUCHI] <i>Five years ago...</i>

00:17:48.969 --> 00:17:50.904
an attack by Rogue Ninja took
<i>the lives...</i>

00:17:50.938 --> 00:17:54.074
<i>of many young shinobi in our</i>
<i>village.</i>

00:17:54.107 --> 00:17:55.342
<i>Shortly afterward...</i>

00:17:57.344 --> 00:17:59.980
So, what is all of this about?

00:18:00.013 --> 00:18:02.683
Just watch and see. You'll be
amazed.

00:18:06.186 --> 00:18:09.089
