00:18:29.843 --> 00:18:31.044
At ease!

00:18:34.381 --> 00:18:35.516
(AMAZED)

00:18:36.717 --> 00:18:38.819
Your thoughts, Kurotsuchi?

00:18:38.852 --> 00:18:40.687
