done?!

00:18:41.688 --> 00:18:42.689
(SHOCKED)

00:18:47.694 --> 00:18:49.763
[ALL] (WORRIED)

00:18:49.796 --> 00:18:50.764
Hey!

00:18:50.797 --> 00:18:52.199
Stop! That's enough!

00:18:53.400 --> 00:18:54.334
I said stop!

00:18:59.673 --> 00:19:00.674
(FRIGHTENED)

00:19:04.845 --> 00:19:06.213
(ATTACKING YELL)

00:19:11.518 --> 00:19:13.220
(STUNNED)

00:19:14.188 --> 00:19:16.190
Please, Grandfather, explain
what this is.

00:19:17.191 --> 00:19:19.259
They're still prototypes...

00:19:19.293 --> 00:19:20.928
But I'm sure if I
make improvements...

00:19:20.961 --> 00:19:23.764
