greatly!

00:19:23.797 --> 00:19:25.098
Next time, I'll be sure-

00:19:25.132 --> 00:19:26.300
[KUROTSUCHI] <i>No.</i>

00:19:26.333 --> 00:19:27.167
(SHOCKED)

00:19:27.201 --> 00:19:30.103
Grandfather, after the War...

00:19:30.137 --> 00:19:33.240
the Five Great Nations conferred
and decided that...

00:19:33.273 --> 00:19:35.242
...we would stand by one
another...

00:19:35.275 --> 00:19:38.245
in the event of an emergency.

00:19:38.278 --> 00:19:41.315
