village?

00:19:58.999 --> 00:20:01.268
Our young shinobi have become
weaker...

00:20:01.301 --> 00:20:04.771
both in skills and in their
spirit.

00:20:04.805 --> 00:20:06.940
If we're faced with a powerful
enemy...

00:20:06.974 --> 00:20:10.244
then they'll be the first
to lose their lives.

00:20:10.277 --> 00:20:12.913
Grandfather, I appreciate your
opinion...

00:20:12.946 --> 00:20:15.415
but I'm the Tsuchikage now.

00:20:15.449 --> 00:20:18.185
(SHOCKED)

00:20:22.055 --> 00:20:25.425
